realised
an
easy
competence
enough
to
secure
the
purchase
of
a
little
estate
adjoining
Highbury,
which
he
had
always
longed
for
enough
to
marry
a
woman
as
portionless
even
as
Miss
Taylor,
and
to
live
according
to
the
wishes
of
his
own
friendly
